name: WarVideos.org
description: WarVideos.org -- WAR is a community-driven decentralized platform empowering independent media and conflict documentation through blockchain technology, enabling global citizens to collaboratively record, verify, and share critical video evidence from regions experiencing geopolitical tensions. The WAR token represents a revolutionary DAO mechanism for supporting transparency, journalistic freedom, and grassroots reporting, allowing token holders to participate in content curation, verification processes, and community governance of an open-source media archive.
